data.description: Welcome to this incredible offering in Panama City, boasting a generous plot of just over 2 acres. This prime corner lot brims with endless possibilities. The standout feature of this property is the marvelous barn/workshop, meticulously constructed in 2019, offering abundant space to pursue all your hobbies and satisfy your storage needs. The fenced perimeter and cross-fencing make it an absolute delight for horse enthusiasts. The delightful brick house, originally built in 1966 and recently renovated in 2023, showcases 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a generously sized family room, and a galley kitchen adorned with stainless steel appliances, new cabinets, and stunning granite counters. Attention builders, take note that the current zoning permits an impressive 5 houses per acre, thus highlighting this property's tremendous investment potential.
